00:09:44,449 --> 00:09:46,349
is gonna be an immediate red flag.

206
00:09:48,430 --> 00:09:49,510
A light nod, you know.

207
00:09:50,437 --> 00:09:53,259
We have this one where she's finally physically assaulted,

208
00:09:54,199 --> 00:09:56,160
and she's terrified, framing again.

209
00:09:56,180 --> 00:09:59,122
And then we have the last one where she unleashes her power

210
00:09:59,142 --> 00:10:00,483
and gets her revenge on these bullies.

211
00:10:01,964 --> 00:10:05,466
And already we can see we've got multiple different frames,

212
00:10:05,546 --> 00:10:06,546
multiple different attitudes,

213
00:10:06,566 --> 00:10:09,408
multiple different themes coming through this one costume.

214
00:10:10,929 --> 00:10:11,969
So if we just break these down,

