00:10:11,989 --> 00:10:13,590
I've got a quick little breakdown for them.

216
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:14,391
So it starts in your school,

217
00:10:14,411 --> 00:10:17,713
we've got hopeful, nervous, excited.

