00:11:03,390 --> 00:11:04,911
I think is a really powerful vision.

238
00:11:06,487 --> 00:11:09,228
For this one here, we've got scared, in pain, intimidated,

239
00:11:09,589 --> 00:11:10,589
pretty obvious again,

240
00:11:11,050 --> 00:11:12,771
she's pressured into one side of the screen.

241
00:11:13,351 --> 00:11:15,032
We've got parts of the bully in the foreground

