00:11:17,134 --> 00:11:18,474
which is also very powerful.

244
00:11:19,335 --> 00:11:21,016
And we've pulled the camera in a lot tighter.

245
00:11:21,577 --> 00:11:22,897
So this is a lot more intense,

246
00:11:23,258 --> 00:11:26,059
and as an audience, we're with her at this point.

247
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,721
These are all fairly obvious things

248
00:11:27,781 --> 00:11:30,102
were for people that are involved in cinematography.

249
00:11:31,023 --> 00:11:33,484
But I think for me, this is the type of stuff

250
00:11:33,524 --> 00:11:34,565
that over the last couple of years,

251
