00:43:26,044 --> 00:43:30,045
So most of you are familiar with concepts

838
00:43:30,325 --> 00:43:33,086
like strong silhouettes, color theory,

839
00:43:33,246 --> 00:43:35,226
abstract shapes, and main character traits,

