00:45:07,505 --> 00:45:08,485
because that's all you're gonna see.

875
00:45:08,505 --> 00:45:09,985
You're not gonna see much of the torso.

876
00:45:10,526 --> 00:45:13,086
So from a character design perspective,

877
00:45:13,166 --> 00:45:14,647
he might seem fairly plain.

878
00:45:16,690 --> 00:45:19,432
This is a character clearly designed for low resolutions

