00:45:35,579 --> 00:45:36,199
I mean,

885
00:45:38,167 --> 00:45:40,228
You can see that the shield is carrying on the back,

886
00:45:40,329 --> 00:45:42,270
and you have that nice big belt going there,

887
00:45:42,330 --> 00:45:44,412
but it does actually serve a purpose.

888
00:45:45,032 --> 00:45:46,453
It shows that the center of mass

889
00:45:46,694 --> 00:45:48,215
