905
00:46:28,837 --> 00:46:30,398
Some rules of thumb for design theory.

906
00:46:31,270 --> 00:46:33,991
Now, there's some simple rules I want to bring attention to.

907
00:46:34,431 --> 00:46:36,371
Again, you're probably familiar with practices

908
00:46:36,431 --> 00:46:38,212
like outlines and body shapes and all of that.

909
00:46:38,932 --> 00:46:40,332
So I want to bring attention to two of them.

910
00:46:41,912 --> 00:46:44,053
Repeated color blocks and consistent patterns.

911
00:46:45,533 --> 00:46:47,534
Now, finding color blocks is really simple

912
00:46:47,834 --> 00:46:49,294
and is a good rule of thumb for any design.

913
00:46:49,714 --> 00:46:52,535
So the gist is that you pick a certain set of colors

914
00:46:52,555 --> 00:46:54,375
for your character and make sure they're repeated

915
00:46:54,395 --> 00:46:55,735
throughout the design pleasingly.

916
00:46:56,795 --> 00:46:59,356
I think Street Fighter is a pretty good example of that.

917
00:47:00,669 --> 00:47:02,389
Notice that most of the characters here,

918
00:47:02,750 --> 00:47:04,870
the colors are repeated more than once,

919
00:47:05,190 --> 00:47:06,750
and usually takes up a large space.

920
00:47:07,510 --> 00:47:10,131
So picking too many colors can feel busy and inconsistent.

921
00:47:10,411 --> 00:47:12,211
Of course, it depends on what kind of project you're doing.

922
00:47:15,872 --> 00:47:16,932
Lost my train of thought here.

923
00:47:19,253 --> 00:47:22,633
If something feels off, or it feels inconsistent,

924
00:47:22,993 --> 00:47:25,234
do a quick color check to see if any of the colors

925
00:47:25,314 --> 00:47:27,714
are actually repeated, or you're adding redundant color.

926
00:47:28,474 --> 00:47:29,915
Or, for that matter, if they're too similar.

927
00:47:30,925 --> 00:47:33,605
You can also break the rules by adding a focus color.

928
00:47:34,025 --> 00:47:36,326
Now, your color choices can be nice and spread out,

929
00:47:36,526 --> 00:47:39,166
but having a single dominant color without repetition

930
00:47:39,186 --> 00:47:40,447
can be surprisingly satisfying.

